width sampled by a 200 MHz digitizer with significant contribution of very\nhigh and very low frequencies. These events may not origin from cosmic ray\nshowers but can be human-made contaminations. The engine of the wavelet\nanalysis can be implemented into the modern powerful FPGA and can remove\nsuspicious events on-line to reduce the trigger rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jun 2014 18:57:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-21"}
