ation of the\nresources versus effectiveness and risk that spacecraft engineers need to work\nwith in designing radiation protection for long-duration human space missions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jun 2014 19:34:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Jun 2014 14:55:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
