r disks with a contamination lower than\n20%. However, mergers cannot be differentiated from the irregular morphological\nclass using these parameters, due to increasingly asymmetry of non-interacting\nlate-type galaxies at z>1. Our automated procedure is applied to the CANDELS\nGOODS-S field and compared with the visual classification recently released on\nthe same area getting similar results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jun 2014 20:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-06"}
