 constraint that can be used to build a bag model. In the non\nAbelian case the confining boundary conditions hold at a specific surface of a\ndomain wall.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jun 2014 10:01:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jun 2014 11:39:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
